nodes.text: S. Moshuddaa was a journalist affiliated with the Hutt-run financial NewsNet, the Nal Hutta Kal'tamok. Moshuddaa reported on several stories during the Galactic Civil War, including Spaaga Core, Inc.'s move into the Corusca stone market. S. Moshuddaa subsequently produced for the Nal Hutta Kal'tamok an in-depth analysis of the various newsfeeds available during the Galactic Civil War.
S. Moshuddaa's byline in "Annual NewsNet Summary" in Star Wars Adventure Journal 11 is spelled as "S. Moshudda."
